>> source: https://www.simplyscratch.com/homemade-ranch-dressing-mix/
>> total time: 5 minutes

In a #mixing bowl{}; measure and add in the @dry buttermilk{1%cup} with @dried parsley{2.5%Tbsp} @dried chives{2%Tbsp}, @dried dill{2%tsp}, @garlic powder{2.5%tsp}, @onion powder{1.5%tsp}, @dried onion flakes{1.5%tsp}, @salt{2%tsp}, @black pepper{1/2%tsp}, @paprika{1/2%tsp}, and @cayenne{1/4%tsp} whisking to combine.

Transfer the ranch mix into a jar or container that has a tight-fitting lid.

Store in the fridge for up to 12 months.
